snippet.title: the Tragedy of Fantastic Beasts the Crimes of Grindelwald "Johnny Depp" - PJ Explained
snippet.description:
I think as the prequel movies go all what the fans really wanted, is a revisit of the known and finding out tidbits we weren’t aware of before, with a whole new story that complements the original series and not take away from it but actually adds. I didn’t really hate this movie. 

I think this movie, as said by everyone else, would have been far greater if made with an experienced screenwriter to help Rowling and a better director, although I still don’t think Rowling would have butcher her own vision if she was not pressured in writing those fan service moments, the kind of pressure she was not experienced in dealing with when working as a novel writer or a producer on the potter films. #FantasticBeasts #JohnnyDepp #PJExplained
